lead_paragraph: Simona Halep did something no one else was able to do against Serena Williams at the U.S. Open on Wednesday but still could not stop the world number one from advancing to the semi-finals of the year's final grand slam.

headline.print_headline: Williams Fights Off Halep to Reach U.S. Open Semi-Finals
